Package model

Class Computer

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Computer

  • public class Computer
extends java.lang.Object
    Computer is the class that represent a computer. A computer is characterized by the following informations:
    • A unique identifier assigned automatically.
    • A name.
    • An introduced date.
    • A discontinued date.
    • A company identifiant.
    Author:
    elgharbi
